tool_input.script:
export const meta = {
  name: 'qa-semantic-search',
  description: 'Execute semantic search for QA workflow',
  phases: [
    { title: 'SemanticSearch', detail: 'Search knowledge files for relevant sections' }
  ]
}

phase('SemanticSearch')

const result = await agent(
  `Execute the semantic search workflow defined in workflows/semantic-search.md.

Working directory: /home/tie303177/work/nabledge/work2/.claude/skills/nabledge-6

Search query: "OS日時ではなく業務上の日付を取得する方法はあるか？締め処理でシステム日時と業務日付を分けて管理したい（目的: 実装したい）"

Steps to follow:
1. Read the file workflows/semantic-search.md to understand the search procedure
2. Execute the semantic search according to that workflow
3. For each page you consider, record why it was selected or skipped
4. For each section, record why it was selected (high/partial) or skipped

Return a JSON object with:
{
  "selected_sections": [
    {"file": "<full path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "relevance": "<high|partial>", "reason": "<why selected>"}
  ],
  "selected_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why selected>"}
  ],
  "excluded_pages": [
    {"path": "<page path relative to knowledge/>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}
  ],
  "excluded_sections": [
    {"file": "<file path>", "section_id": "<sN>", "reason": "<why skipped>"}
  ]
}`,
  {
    label: 'semantic-search',
    phase: 'SemanticSearch',
    schema: {
      type: 'object',
      properties: {
        selected_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              relevance: { type: 'string', enum: ['high', 'partial'] },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'relevance', 'reason']
          }
        },
        selected_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_pages: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              path: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['path', 'reason']
          }
        },
        excluded_sections: {
          type: 'array',
          items: {
            type: 'object',
            properties: {
              file: { type: 'string' },
              section_id: { type: 'string' },
              reason: { type: 'string' }
            },
            required: ['file', 'section_id', 'reason']
          }
        }
      },
      required: ['selected_sections', 'selected_pages', 'excluded_pages', 'excluded_sections']
    }
  }
)

return result
